---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="mt-32 border-t border-accent-gray-100 bg-accent-gray-50">
  <div class="container-x py-12">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
      <div class="md:col-span-2">
        <a href={base} class="inline-block mb-4" aria-label="aidigest.club home">
          <img
            src={`${base}logo-compact.svg`}
            alt="aidigest.club"
            class="h-8 w-auto"
            width="480"
            height="80"
          />
        </a>
        <p class="text-sm text-accent-gray-700 leading-relaxed max-w-md">
          每日 AI 行业动态摘要——覆盖热点新闻、企业级实践、AI Coding 与深度报告。
          内容由 AI 辅助整理，每日清晨自动更新。
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4 class="text-xs uppercase font-bold tracking-wider text-accent-gray-500 mb-3">导航</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li><a href={base} class="hover:text-accent-purple transition-colors">最新日报</a></li>
          <li><a href={`${base}archive/`} class="hover:text-accent-purple transition-colors">历史归档</a></li>
          <li><a href={`${base}about/`} class="hover:text-accent-purple transition-colors">关于本站</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4 class="text-xs uppercase font-bold tracking-wider text-accent-gray-500 mb-3">说明</h4>
        <p class="text-xs text-accent-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-2">
          Jason’s Personal Project.
        </p>
        <img
          src={`${base}jason-signature.png`}
          alt="Jason’s Signature"
          class="block w-auto h-auto"
          style="max-width: 200px;"
          width="200"
          height="59"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-10 pt-8 border-t border-accent-gray-300 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center justify-between gap-2">
      <p class="text-xs text-accent-gray-500">
        © {year} aidigest.club · Built with Astro · Hosted on GitHub Pages
      </p>
      <p class="text-xs text-accent-gray-500">
        内容仅供参考，不构成投资建议
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
